import React from 'react'
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'
import { Collapse, Container, Navbar, NavbarToggler } from 'reactstrap'


const AppNavbar = () => {
    return (
         <>
        <Navbar>
            <Container>
                <Link to="/" className="text-white text-decoration-none">
                        Brownie
                </Link>
                    <NavbarToggler />
                    <Collapse></Collapse>
            </Container>
        </Navbar>
        </>
    )
   
}

export default AppNavbar;
